        {
          "username": "Dara Filut",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "103652581591498814574",
          "user_review_count": 4,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTIC7XS2PCb2zWXhffqDmoFEI3eIHLnSWtpPbNitMHHMPF-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I made an appointment expecting to be seen within a reasonable timeframe, but ended up waiting over an hour past my scheduled appointment time. I understand that urgent cares can get busy and occasional delays happen, but appointments don\u2019t seem very meaningful if patients are still waiting this long.\n\nIt also appeared that the location was extremely short staffed, with only one physician working, and the provider seemed understandably overwhelmed trying to manage the volume of patients. I do feel for the staff, but the long wait and lack of communication made for a frustrating experience overall. Unfortunately, based on this visit, I would not return.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21VeWF6VnljVTV2T1RGWUxUUjRZbDlCWDE5eE1XYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xdf0e39ddde0873ab!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmUyazVycU5vOTFYLTR4Yl9BX19xMWc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "a month ago",
