          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_oiuqXql0_EJXSF-alfFX53waMbApdyruYn15GGP_smG5tTlh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Pathetic service. If you need to be seen don\u2019t come here. I was referred on from the 50th street because I needed an X-ray on my chest. The waiting room emptied only to fill and empty again. Went multiple times to the front desk to ask if I would be seen. Her responses was there are people are ahead of you. A door dash delivery driver came in to drop off food. When the front desk women went to hand it off she asked the RN \u201cis Jeff able to see someone for a x-ray\u201d the RN responded \u201che is free\u201d. I waited another 20 min to be seen from that interaction that I over heard.",
